&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;7&quot;&gt;We are looking for an&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;strong data-path-to-node=&quot;7&quot; data-index-in-node=&quot;22&quot;&gt;Associate Creative Director (ACD) of Brand Partnerships&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span class=&quot;Apple-converted-space&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;with deep experience in long-form YouTube content and social media. Your mission is to bridge the gap between our Sales and Creative teams, ensuring brand integrations feel like a value-add to our audience rather than a commercial break.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p data-path-to-node=&quot;8&quot;&gt;You aren’t just making ads; you are protecting the integrity of our YouTube and social content while successfully weaving in brand messaging. This role requires a &quot;writer-first&quot; creative who can capture the specific DP voice and pivot seamlessly between internal brainstorming and client-facing pitches.&lt;/p&gt;
